e>
<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Apameia</placeName></head><div type="edition" lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><div type="textpart" n="r" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>κυρίᾳ μου καὶ ἐπιποθήτῃ θείᾳ, Τάρη 

    <lb n="2"/>θυγάτηρ ἀδελφῆς σου Ἀλλοῦτος 

    <lb n="3"/>ἐν <expan>θ<ex cert="high">ε</ex></expan>ῷ χαίρειν. 

    <lb n="4"/>πρὸ παντὸς <choice><corr>εὔχομαι</corr><sic>ευχομε</sic></choice> τῷ <expan>θ<ex cert="high">ε</ex></expan>ῷ <choice><corr>ὑγιαίνουσάν</corr><sic>υγιενουσαν</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="5"/>σε καὶ εὐθυμοῦσαν <choice><corr>ἀπολαβεῖν</corr><sic>απολαβιν</sic></choice> τὰ παρ᾽ ἐμοῦ 

    <lb n="6"/>γράμματα· αὕτη γὰρ μού ἐστιν εὐχή. γί-


    <lb n="7"/><choice><corr>γνωσκε</corr><sic>γεινωσκε</sic></choice> δέ, κυρία μου, ὅτι ἀπὸ τῶν <expan>Πάσχω<ex cert="high">ν</ex></expan> 

    <lb n="8"/>ἡ μήτηρ μου, ἡ ἀδελφή σου, ἐτελε<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ύτη</supplied>σεν. 

    <lb n="9"/>ὅ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">τ</supplied>ε δὲ τὴν μητέρα μου εἶχα, μεθ᾽ <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ἑ</supplied>αυτῆς 

    <lb n="10"/>ὅλον τὸ γένος μου αὕτη ἦν· ἀφ᾽ οὗ δ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ὲ</supplied> ἐτε-

    <lb n="11"/>λεύτησ<add place="supralinear">ε</add><subst><add place="inline">ν</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">ετελευτησ<del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable">α</del>ν</del></subst>, <choice><corr>ἔμεινα</corr><sic>εμινα</sic></choice> ἔρημος, μ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">η</supplied>δένα ἔχουσα 

    <lb n="12"/>ἐπὶ ξένοις τόποις. μνημόνευε οὖν, 

    <lb n="13"/>θεία, ὡς ζητούσης τῆς μητρός μου, <choice><corr>ἵνα</corr><sic>εινα</sic></choice> εἴ τι-

    <lb n="14"/>να <choice><corr>εὑρίσκεις</corr><sic>ευρισκις</sic></choice> πέμπε πρὸς ἐμέ. προσα-

    <lb n="15"/>γόρευε πᾶσαν τὴν <choice><corr>συγγένειαν</corr><sic>συγγενιαν</sic></choice> ἡμῶν. 

    <lb n="16"/>ἐρρωμένην σε ὁ <expan>κ<ex cert="high">ύριο</ex></expan>ς διαφυ-

    <lb n="17"/>λάττοι μακροῖς καὶ εἰρη-

    <lb n="18"/>νικοῖς χρόνοις, κυρία μου. 
</ab></div><div type="textpart" n="v" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="19"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ἀπό</supplied>δος τὴν ἐπιστολὴν 

    <lb n="20"/>Ὡρείνᾳ, ἀδελφῇ Ἀπολλωνίου, <choice><corr>Κοπτιτίσσῃ</corr><sic>κοπτιτισα</sic></choice>, παρὰ 

    <lb n="21"/>Τάρης, θυγατρὸς ἀδελφῆς αὐτῆς, ἀπὸ <choice><corr>Ἀπαμείας</corr><sic>απαμιας</sic></choice>. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.32904" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.32904" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" notBefore="301" notAfter="500">IV - V</date></p></div><div n="meta.32904" type="commentary" subtype="general" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>Zur Datierung vgl. BL II 2, S. 35.</p></div><div n="meta.32904" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Bour.</title><biblScope type="numbers">25</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">32904</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0082</series>; ; <biblScope type="numbers">25</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0082;;25" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.32904" type="bibliography" subtype="illustrations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><bibl type="illustration" default="NO">Pl. III</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.32904" type="bibliography" subtype="otherPublications" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Andere Publikationen</head><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="other" default="NO">Sel. Pap. I 165</bibl><bibl type="publication" subtype="other" default="NO">Naldini, Cristianesimo 78</bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.32904" type="bibliography" subtype="translations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Übersetzungen</head><listBibl lang="de" default="NO"><head lang="de">Deutsch:</head><bibl type="translations" default="NO">Metzger, Nachrichten aus dem Wüstensan